titleStmt.title: A list of the knights, citizens, burgesses, and barons of the Cinque-ports that are return'd to serve in the Parliament of England, to begin the 17th. and then to be adjourn'd to the 30th. of October 1679. Note, that those that have this mark (dagger) after them, were not members of the last Parlaiment.
Lists. 1679-10-17.
